[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "……ここが、一番奥ですよね？\nお宝も、誰かの気配もなさそう……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……残念だけど、何もないみたいね。\nさっき戦った魔物も、伝承とは関係なさそうだったし",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "ウソー！　劇にもなってる伝承なのに！　\n宝箱のひとつもないなんて、拍子抜けだよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "伝承ってそういうものよ。嘘であれ真であれ、\n語り継がれるうちに、どんどん大きくなるもの",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "そっか……残念",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "それに……これは私の推測だけど、\nここには元々、お宝なんてなかったのかもしれない",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "え？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "伝承は、ここまでの道筋を示すようなものだった。\n竜の牙も含めてね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "伝わる人には伝わる、暗号のような筆致だった。\n……恐らくこれは、この場所への秘密の暗号だったのよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "友人か、恋人か……詳しいことは分からないけれど、\nきっと誰かが秘密の場所として使っていたのかもね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "わぁ……だとしたら、なんだか素敵ですね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "うん、そうね……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "ねぇ、見て。この地面、普通の岩じゃない。\n希少な鉱石が混じってる",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "こっちの水草も、陸じゃ見たことない種類。\n錬金術の素材に使えそう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "わっ、ほんと！？　さっすがミルカ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "ふふ、ミルカさん、目が輝いてる",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……シャリー、うるさい",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ふふ、みんな楽しそうね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……ここは素材の宝庫ね。\n採取したいものが、たくさん",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "ねえ、あたしも採取する！　\nどれが一番すごい素材？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "その青い結晶、触らないで。\n壊れやすいから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "あっ、ごめんごめん！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "ユリエさん、紀行文のメモですか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ええ……伝承のお宝はなかったけれど、\nここに来た価値は十分にあったわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……姉さん、私のことは書いてないでしょうね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "あら、ダメかしら。\nあなたたちと一緒に来た記録も、きっと誰かの役に立つ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "あたしのことも書いてよ！　\n「伝承のお宝　探し隊」とか、かっこよく書いてね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ふふ、考えておくわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……これだけ集まれば十分。\n思いがけず、いい素材に出会えた",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "ミルカさん、その素材で\n何を作るか決まってるんですか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "ええ、そうね……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ミルカ、どうかした？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "いいえ、何も",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "8971561709699782619",
		"text": "何を調合するにせよ、手が必要だったら呼んでね！\n手伝うよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "シャリステラ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallistera",
		"model_path_hash": "8814674670384979784",
		"text": "わたしもお手伝いします！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2239883848991404562",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "うん。二人とも、ありがとう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]